---
title: Harvest Turkey Sheet Pan with Kale and Gravy
description: Harvest sheet pan dinner for the win! Roasted squash, tender and crisp kale, caramelized onions, all topped with savoury gravy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/harvest-turkey-sheet-pan-cb2b7ac0.jpg
